data.description: Welcome to this move in ready home! Well maintained single-level home in Cordova! This home features 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, central heat and cooling. Huge backyard with access to the Greenline! Just minutes away from restaurants, shopping centers, schools and more!!! Easy to show. Best of all no HOA. Nice home with great potential awaits your finishing touches. Call today for a private showing!
